"""Test method to search images."""
class MockBrowser(object):
    """Mock browser to replace selenium driver."""

    def __init__(self, html_f):
        self.page_source = html_f.read()
        self.page_source = self.page_source.decode('utf8') if 'decode' in dir(
            self.page_source) else self.page_source

    def get(self, url):
        pass

    def quit(self):
        pass
google.images.get_browser_with_url = Mock(return_value=MockBrowser(html_f))
res = google.search_images('apple', num_images=10)
self.assertEqual(len(res), 10)
load_html_file('html_files')
